## Overview

This task file will contain all tasks related to implementing the Metrics and Analytics functionality for the Dashboard Management System. This includes:

- Business metrics tracking (revenue, appointments, customers, employees, services)
- Data visualization (KPI cards, charts, graphs)
- Date range filtering and period comparison
- Export capabilities (CSV, PDF)
- Real-time metrics updates

